+#### `float-above-fullscreen`
+
+<sup>Since: next release</sup>
+
+Make a floating window always visible when the current workspace is occupied by a fullscreen window.
+
+```kdl
+window-rule {
+    float-above-fullscreen false
+}
+```
+
